data.description: COME CHECK OUT THIS GEM! Nestled within the peaceful surroundings of Ashley Hills in Summerville, this lovely ranch-style home is a true sanctuary. With 1450 square feet of living space, this residence offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan effortlessly flows from room to room, accommodating an easy and relaxed lifestyle. Complementing the 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms are vaulted ceilings, adding an airy touch to the interior. Tucked away on a cul-de-sac lot, privacy is guaranteed, and the 2-car garage provides ample space for storage. The expansive lot presents an opportunity for outdoor recreation! Embrace the comfort and serenity of this idyllic property.
